## Rules

- Always try to use the shadcn/ui library.
- Always try to use framer-motion.
- You must use Tailwind CSS for styling.
- You must install any ShadcnUI missing component with `pnpm dlx shadcn@2.3.0 add <component-name />`. dont change / add flags / modify the command
- Wait longer for the install command output. It should output "Created X file" or "Skipped x files" if the component already existed. "Skipped x files" is also a success. 
- Follow Shadcn UI component guidelines and best practices.
- Ensure UI is responsive and accessible.

